statements.sql: select exists(select * from `workspace_members` where `user_id` = 1 and `workspace_members`.`deleted_at` is null) as `exists`

select * from `boards` where exists (select * from `workspaces` where `boards`.`workspace_id` = `workspaces`.`id` and exists (select * from `workspace_members` where `workspaces`.`id` = `workspace_members`.`workspace_id` and `is_active` = 1 and `user_id` = 1 and `workspace_members`.`deleted_at` is null))
select * from `board_members` where `is_accept_invite` = 0 and `board_members`.`board_id` in (1) and `board_members`.`deleted_at` is null

select * from `workspace_members` where `workspace_id` in (select `workspace_id` from `workspace_members` where `user_id` = 1 and `is_active` = 1) and `deleted_at` is null and `workspace_members`.`deleted_at` is null
select * from `board_members` where `is_accept_invite` = 0 and `board_members`.`board_id` in (1) and `deleted_at` is null and `board_members`.`deleted_at` is null

select * from `tasks` where `catalog_id` in (select `catalogs`.`id` from `catalogs` inner join `boards` on `catalogs`.`board_id` = `boards`.`id` inner join `workspaces` on `boards`.`workspace_id` = `workspaces`.`id` inner join `workspace_members` on `workspaces`.`id` = `workspace_members`.`workspace_id` where `workspace_members`.`user_id` = 1 and `workspace_members`.`is_active` = 1 and `workspace_members`.`deleted_at` is null) and `tasks`.`deleted_at` is null
select * from `activity_log` where json_unquote(json_extract(`properties`, '$."workspace_id"')) in (1) order by `created_at` desc
